{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"73ac9982f5","title":"准备在邹、滕地区打大歼灭战","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"84063caeda","index":0,"year":1945,"month":10,"day":31,"articleId":"73ac9982f5"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji4","name":"毛泽东文集第四卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji4.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji4":{"comments":[{"id":"046eecb063","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"73ac9982f5","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"根据毛泽东手稿刊印。"},{"id":"62f005f4c1","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"73ac9982f5","index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":6,"text":"邹、滕，指山东邹县和滕县。"},{"id":"51f080d12e","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"73ac9982f5","index":2,"part_index":1,"offset":3,"text":"陈，指陈毅，当时任新四军军长兼山东军区司令员。黎，指黎玉，当时任山东军区副政治委员。"},{"id":"b99c804d9b","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"73ac9982f5","index":3,"part_index":2,"offset":5,"text":"临城，今山东枣庄市薛城。"},{"id":"70a01d4e90","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"73ac9982f5","index":4,"part_index":2,"offset":8,"text":"陈大庆（一九○五——一九七三），江西崇义人。当时任国民党军第十九集团军总司令。"},{"id":"23f0878a6e","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"73ac9982f5","index":5,"part_index":2,"offset":100,"text":"恩县，一九五六年撤销，辖区分别划归山东平原、夏津和武城三县。"},{"id":"f1e1b7b956","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"73ac9982f5","index":6,"part_index":2,"offset":153,"text":"霍守义，当时任国民党军第十二军军长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"1acaae55c1","type":"title","text":"准备在邹、滕地区打大歼灭战","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"73ac9982f5"},{"id":"62f005f4c1","type":"appellation","text":"陈、黎：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"73ac9982f5"},{"id":"51f080d12e","type":"paragraph","text":"据息，临城陈大庆九十七军以护路为任务，若干天内似无强大后续力量。惟邹、滕地区蒋介石在所必争，必将增兵北进，我以主力位于该区，准备打大歼灭战是完全必要的。渤海军区在德州南北占领两段铁路，占领黄河涯、恩县，歼灭一部敌伪，具有很大意义。望令该军区扩大铁路占领区，发动民众公私兼顾，掘毁路基，并集中注意于歼灭霍守义十二军。该军似急于赴东北，决不应让其过去。为此目的，请考虑增加该方面兵力，并加强作战指导。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"73ac9982f5"},{"id":"b99c804d9b","type":"paragraph","text":"军 委","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"73ac9982f5"},{"id":"70a01d4e90","type":"paragraph","text":"酉世","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"73ac9982f5"}],"page":{"id":"727fe52d70","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"73ac9982f5","start":69,"end":69}}}},"__N_SSG":true}